  <brief_title>In Vivo Molecular Imaging Predicts Therapeutic Response in Ulcerative Colitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>In Vivo Molecular Imaging With Infliximab Antibody With FITC Predicts Therapeutic Response in Ulcerative Colitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
