  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Molecular imaging with infliximab antibody with FITC has the potential to predict therapeutic
      responses to infliximab antibody and can be used for personalized medicine in ulcerative
      colitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Recruiting</overall_status>
